359
00:26:20,160 --> 00:26:23,120
So can I

360
00:26:23,360 --> 00:26:25,280
ask you a favor?

361
00:26:26,600 --> 00:26:27,840
That female bandit?

362
00:26:33,400 --> 00:26:34,440
She’s a cannibal.

363
00:26:34,640 --> 00:26:35,760
I can’t make it.

364
00:26:35,760 --> 00:26:37,840
Don’t you

365
